<subSubSection pageId="6" pageNumber="297" type="diagnosis">
<paragraph blockId="6.[828,1437,358,605]" pageId="6" pageNumber="297">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[828,1075,358,381]" pageId="6" pageNumber="297">Differential diagnosis.</emphasis>
The largest of known Guatemalan species (body length 
<quantity box="[1060,1221,390,413]" metricMagnitude="-3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="3.705" metricValueMax="3.85" metricValueMin="3.56" pageId="6" pageNumber="297" unit="mm" value="3.705" valueMax="3.85" valueMin="3.56">3.56–3.85 mm</quantity>
), recognized by the combination of the body size, the densely punctate pronotum with deep foveae, the elytral sculpture, having a very large callus on the 5 
<superScript attach="left" box="[1048,1060,485,499]" fontSize="6" pageId="6" pageNumber="297">th</superScript>
interstria, the 3 
<superScript attach="left" box="[1232,1245,485,499]" fontSize="6" pageId="6" pageNumber="297">rd</superScript>
interstria slightly raised over the basal ¼, and the 4 
<superScript attach="left" box="[1185,1197,517,531]" fontSize="6" pageId="6" pageNumber="297">th</superScript>
interstria raised in the area anterior to 5 
<superScript attach="left" box="[1013,1025,549,563]" fontSize="6" pageId="6" pageNumber="297">th</superScript>
callus, and the male genitalia (
<figureCitation box="[1364,1430,550,573]" captionStart="Fig" captionStartId="6.[151,182,2059,2078]" captionTargetBox="[215,1372,635,2037]" captionTargetId="figure@6.[214,1372,635,2037]" captionTargetPageId="6" captionText="Fig. 5. Hydrochus pertuberculatus sp. nov., habitus and male genitalia of holotype." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3879772" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/3879772/files/figure.png" pageId="6" pageNumber="297">Fig. 5</figureCitation>
; described below).
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<caption ID-DOI="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3879772" ID-Zenodo-Dep="3879772" box="[151,859,2059,2078]" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/3879772/files/figure.png" pageId="6" pageNumber="297" startId="6.[151,182,2059,2078]" targetBox="[215,1372,635,2037]" targetPageId="6">
<paragraph blockId="6.[151,859,2059,2078]" box="[151,859,2059,2078]" pageId="6" pageNumber="297">
